    14→ * object loader is invoked.
    15→ * @author Stephen Wong
    16→ *
    17→ * @param <ReturnT>  The type of object to be created.
    18→ */
    19→public class ObjectLoader<ReturnT> extends AObjectLoader<ReturnT> {
    20→
    21→	/**
    22→	 * Lambda function to return an error object of type ReturnT
    23→	 */
    24→	private BiFunction<String, Object[], ReturnT> errorFac;
    25→//	private Function<Object[], ReturnT> errorFac;
    26→	
    27→
    28→	/**
    29→	 * Constructor for the class.   The given errorFac is used to generate instances when the loadInstance() method
    30→	 * is otherwise unable to do so because of a processing error.
    31→	 * @param errorFac A factory method that takes the same array of input parameters that loadInstance() 
    32→	 * takes and returns an instance of ReturnT.
    33→	 */
    34→	@Deprecated
    35→	public ObjectLoader(Function<Object[], ReturnT> errorFac) {
    36→		// Wrap errorFac in a BiFunction and delegate to the other constructor.
    37→		this((classname, args) -> { 
